<title key="Chicken, roasted, with pears and sauce">Ein guet richt von <ingredient en="chicken" commodity="Q864693">huner</ingredient></title> 
<instruction>NIm <ingredient en="chicken" commodity="Q864693">huner</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>prat die mit vollen gar endleich</instruction> 
<instruction>zu mursel sie</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>lasz sieden nuer in <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">smalcz</ingredient> vnd in ein wenig <ingredient en="water" commodity="Q283">wasser</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction><ingredient en="bread crust" commodity="Q990859">rinten pratz</ingredient> nym <ingredient en="ginger" commodity="Q15046077">Ingwers</ingredient> vnd ein wenig <ingredient en="pepper" commodity="Q3143131">pheffers</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="anise" commodity="Q33873455">anais</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>das mal mit <ingredient en="vinegar" commodity="Q41354">esseich</ingredient> zu samen vnd mit dem selbem sod</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>nym vir gepraten <alternative reason="ingredient"><ingredient en="pear" commodity="Q13099586">pieren</ingredient> oder <ingredient en="quince" commodity="Q2751465">kuten</ingredient></alternative></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>das <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">condiment</dish> tue dar czue dewu <ingredient en="chicken" commodity="Q864693">huner</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>lasz ez sieden gar wol damit das es obem dikch werd</instruction> vnd <closer>gib ez hin</closer></div></body></text></TEI>